Edit file /etc/sysconfig/network/ifcfg-&lt;Interface-Name&gt; and setup following value
    </para>
    <programlisting>
<![CDATA[IPADDR="<ipv6-Adresse>/<prefix>"
]]>
    </programlisting>

    </sect3>

    <sect3>
     <title>
Additional information
    </title>
    <para>
See file /usr/share/doc/packages/sysconfig/Network 
    </para>

    </sect3>


